"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c3319ad9a39d5b88f9d8e31548b9bedb142e377","tid":411564,"uid":20170,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T04:25:21.000Z","msg":"中國式和平<br />\n只要置於中華統治下 就有和平 否則就係外虜 雖遠必誅 誅撚完你 收歸旗下 咪同你一家人和平囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2df364aef98cc323ccb12e42b38e18c88d3d2753","tid":411564,"uid":42764,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T04:27:41.000Z","msg":"由93年加入中化科，就諗住搞死香港教育<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6da10f0492d309feb4539bf52dfe12df4264fea","tid":411564,"uid":80966,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T04:32:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e04b029aa6259648ad8d5fc10f919173065abf8a","tid":411564,"uid":37735,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T04:32:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由93年加入中化科，就諗住搞死香港教育<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n根本香港好多野可以刪除<br />\n<br />\n果6篇中化 用學術來講<br />\n一堆吹水野 假野"},{"pid":"2c37c7ce6512b2111cb8b83272968ea0185a3e7d","tid":411564,"uid":42764,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T04:38:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>由93年加入中化科，就諗住搞死香港教育<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n根本香港好多野可以刪除<br />\n<br />\n果6篇中化 用學術來講<br />\n一堆吹水野 假野</blockquote><br />\nDSE範文都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44b8e54b585411350a334277b78f2c9289411749","tid":411564,"uid":22858,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T04:47:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.libertarianprepper.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/double_standards_3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.libertarianprepper.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2012%2F09%2Fdouble_standards_3.png&h=a73a6df0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6945b89b07a190e3608dcbd2c2f49